Empath::

The Decepticon femme enters the medbay and looks quizzically at 
Lizzie/Sanguine and Amperion.  "You two need some quarters on this 
ship, I'm assuming?"  Once again, she positions herself so the 
symbols on her wings are prominently displayed.
